{"tid":235512,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"接左unity freelance半年,你問我答","createTime":"2017-05-09T05:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T11:26:46.000Z","uid":115538,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"65158a7d4f14a153f9622b51bea292b6a9ff24f1","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0417cb39b31f34d78279caa47b8af7eefe3f3d6f","tid":235512,"uid":17204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T05:37:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請唔請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68349c2f5442994947a80a35768a17fae8a70ca7","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T05:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請唔請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係獨立工作者黎,亦都冇諗住開工作室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a27de5d2ca92149d2b1b93fef9d552baf01e19d","tid":235512,"uid":2107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T06:07:44.000Z","msg":"學左幾耐"},{"pid":"6fb93a2a8994db5ab0fea584c02df8e133e51986","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T06:16:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n其實我依加仲係學生黎<img src