c7297cd6d069bfc8af45864","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無作品睇下</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0DdPImn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0DdPImn.jpg&h=1cce8de0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢份就係我上個月交既EA<br />\nAR game黎,其他遊戲截圖有人想睇先再po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a69166d4dd44547ab7f9f5dbf7bc7d790b30ce4","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:43:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n其實我依加仲係學生黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上堂學就學左大約半年,我學第一個月既時侯覺得學得太慢,然後開始一有時間就睇下相關既片同埋自己寫下d program出黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後拎左d作品去見工又真係見得成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔記得講,我本身都有幾種programming底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爸打本身讀咩？</blockquote><br />\n讀緊game and animation,唔係精programming都唔好揀,十個讀完九個冇工開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e92f5956b67adcc87325a45978a3484388b6eb","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:46:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>主要做3d?定玩埋2d,vr,ar?</blockquote><br />\n主做3d, 2d做過既作品一隻手數得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n長期幫緊某公司寫緊d event用既VR同 AR 既 app,因為呢幾年VR同AR都幾流行下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黎緊會再幫間中學寫隻全3d既手機game"},{"pid":"caa80183a2084112ef304683987bb125505d86d5","tid":235512,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:48:21.000Z","msg":"自己搵job完全無靠人脈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fb22e563727cc0a3d34945d25dd62a1cfe983f","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:49:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己搵job完全無靠人脈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係香港接job真係識人好過識字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我基本上全部job都係人脈番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e121490879ea836ae2d2163405bde6d1cb5df9e","tid":235512,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:01:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己搵job完全無靠人脈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係香港接job真係識人好過識字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我基本上全部job都係人脈番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732720e917aed830dd7e2e551ac1f027e7467c72","tid":235512,"uid":2107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:37:10.000Z","msg":"有無咩網介紹黎學下 定鳩睇就得"},{"pid":"f7adc37250994973391f9c8061aaa80632780194","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無咩網介紹黎學下 定鳩睇就得</blockquote><br />\n你有冇programming底?<br />\n如果有既話就真係鳩睇都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果冇我就推薦&quot;陳間時光&quot;呢個youtube channel,雖然d教學好多廢話,但係用左好多生活例子代入coding呢件事到,所以對完全冇底既人黎講幾易理解到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97ea56a063cb7212734bfcc26941330e8f64773","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:54:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無咩網介紹黎學下 定鳩睇就得</blockquote><br />\n你有冇programming底?<br />\n如果有既話就真係鳩睇都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果冇我就推薦&quot;陳間時光&quot;呢個youtube channel,雖然d教學好多廢話,但係用左好多生活例子代入coding呢件事到,所以對完全冇底既人黎講幾易理解到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有個係&quot;unity taiwan&quot;<br />\n呢個youtube channel係官方channel黎,入面既教學可以學到概念,但係學唔到coding,因為佢直接比d code你,冇咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76610afcab14e0aa147e479f4f26924b3a0b88b","tid":235512,"uid":83795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T15:51:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n其實我依加仲係學生黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上堂學就學左大約半年,我學第一個月既時侯覺得學得太慢,然後開始一有時間就睇下相關既片同埋自己寫下d program出黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後拎左d作品去見工又真係見得成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見咩公司請unity developer, 定係見工做freelancer#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f444fcb3da09497c7c2b29d8c0a6442405eb9348","tid":235512,"uid":101706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T19:34:53.000Z","msg":"可以留Tg問野嗎？新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25292021ae541d59870b5187a55f8618e595036c","tid":235512,"uid":57913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T19:40:39.000Z","msg":"點解唔學unreal"},{"pid":"c6d818cba75bd09c085145905593d6ed4a8d3ce2","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:24:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n其實我依加仲係學生黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上堂學就學左大約半年,我學第一個月既時侯覺得學得太慢,然後開始一有時間就睇下相關既片同埋自己寫下d program出黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後拎左d作品去見工又真係見得成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見咩公司請unity developer, 定係見工做freelancer#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該咁講啦,香港做freelancer好麻煩,一星期至少要番公司一兩日,冇得交貨日先交貨或者上水,所以我依加每個星期基本上要走兩三間唔同既公司"},{"pid":"828ad6512063935d28e3517da7c18aeab81e5940","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:35:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以留Tg問野嗎？新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n@UnityChan"},{"pid":"18a13de59ca65686c85f8d0dd9824037e5d6d04e","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:39:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔學unreal</blockquote><br />\n我都有Unreal底,雖然不及Unity<br />\n<br />\n但係最主要既問題係,兩個唔同既Engine既用途都不一,Unreal主打光影同粒子細節度,所以比較食效能,做APP唔太適合<br />\n<br />\n相反Unity比人屌D畫面柒既原因係佢主打跨平台,所以效能方面做得好好<br />\n<br />\n其次就係香港好少Job係做Unreal,因為Unreal真係九成做Game一成自由發揮<br />\n而Unity就係五五波,做唔做Game都得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff98b31adfcc20da9f2e05fdd706142dbc38ca41","tid":235512,"uid":102405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:16:15.000Z","msg":"有無咩 state machine library同埋 network library介紹?<br />\n<br />\nunity support邊隻networking系統? <a href=\"http://socket.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsocket.io&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7502390e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">socket.io</a>用唔用到 <a href=\"http://定一要用.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%81%E7%94%A8.net&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f46848c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">定一要用.net</a>個隻?"},{"pid":"1fb264e459cbbb8922bb31bbf76113987e21ce0b","tid":235512,"uid":76570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"留名學野 我都係係fevawork到學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過自己識畫cg圖 但唔知有冇個優勢到"},{"pid":"4e3cadd5821c47726220de25f3955090ce712dcb","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:41:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無咩 state machine library同埋 network library介紹?<br />\n<br />\nunity support邊隻networking系統? <a href=\"http://socket.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsocket.io&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7502390e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">socket.io</a>用唔用到 <a href=\"http://定一要用.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%81%E7%94%A8.net&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f46848c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">定一要用.net</a>個隻?</blockquote><br />\n我就一般都係用Photon或者Golang呢兩種,一黎Photon泛用性高,二黎Golang支援架設多人伺服器,所以我都係玩呢兩種<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://同埋Unity亦都有內置既.NET\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%90%8C%E5%9F%8BUnity%E4%BA%A6%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E5%85%A7%E7%BD%AE%E6%97%A2.NET&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=8a10a469\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">同埋Unity亦都有內置既.NET</a>可以用,如果唔係要做到一隻好大型既線上遊戲,<a href=\"http://基本上.NET\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8A.NET&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=86d24813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">基本上.NET</a>已經夠做<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://而至於socket.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%80%8C%E8%87%B3%E6%96%BCsocket.io&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=63e75690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">而至於socket.io</a>就一定用到,<a href=\"http://如果我冇記錯Unity係4.3ver之後就有提供socket.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%88%91%E5%86%87%E8%A8%98%E9%8C%AFUnit