ime":"2017-05-10T04:55:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無咩 state machine library同埋 network library介紹?<br />\n<br />\nunity support邊隻networking系統? <a href=\"http://socket.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsocket.io&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7502390e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">socket.io</a>用唔用到 <a href=\"http://定一要用.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%81%E7%94%A8.net&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f46848c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">定一要用.net</a>個隻?</blockquote><br />\n我就一般都係用Photon或者Golang呢兩種,一黎Photon泛用性高,二黎Golang支援架設多人伺服器,所以我都係玩呢兩種<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://同埋Unity亦都有內置既.NET\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%90%8C%E5%9F%8BUnity%E4%BA%A6%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E5%85%A7%E7%BD%AE%E6%97%A2.NET&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=8a10a469\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">同埋Unity亦都有內置既.NET</a>可以用,如果唔係要做到一隻好大型既線上遊戲,<a href=\"http://基本上.NET\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8A.NET&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=86d24813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">基本上.NET</a>已經夠做<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://而至於socket.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%80%8C%E8%87%B3%E6%96%BCsocket.io&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=63e75690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">而至於socket.io</a>就一定用到,<a href=\"http://如果我冇記錯Unity係4.3ver之後就有提供socket.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%88%91%E5%86%87%E8%A8%98%E9%8C%AFUnity%E4%BF%824.3ver%E4%B9%8B%E5%BE%8C%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%89%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9Bsocket.io&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=67bd5f43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">如果我冇記錯Unity係4.3ver之後就有提供socket.io</a>既asset開放比所有使用者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nState Machine 呢， 有無用開咩library?</blockquote><br />\n呢個反而少接觸,都係用Unity內置既Finite,暫時為止未有遇到大問題=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15abc0748db36ce3938195d208e961a9a4b9dcc","tid":235512,"uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T05:24:25.000Z","msg":"巴打黎緊接個隻中學3D game 收佢幾錢<br />\n<br />\n想大約知下咩市價<br />\n<br />\nbtw 巴打係隻秋?  one man band 做哂 game/art/level/story/network design?"},{"pid":"58776df14e1504473d60ef1e153d3a6a543631d6","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T05:30:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打黎緊接個隻中學3D game 收佢幾錢<br />\n<br />\n想大約知下咩市價<br />\n<br />\nbtw 巴打係隻秋?  one man band 做哂 game/art/level/story/network design?</blockquote><br />\n我冇咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係做programming,level design同埋network <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上其他野都係PM佢地傾完再同我講番<br />\n<br />\n至於中學個個唔講住先,因為未confirm既,就以我之前幫另一間中學做既vr app黎講,隻app主要係播一段英文或者係播片然後尋物,有限時有計分(當然係vr視點)<br />\n<br />\n實收都有五位數既,做就大約2個禮拜"},{"pid":"b78d2d968835797f4d17a41f80ec2bf0afe16a64","tid":235512,"uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T05:50:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打黎緊接個隻中學3D game 收佢幾錢<br />\n<br />\n想大約知下咩市價<br />\n<br />\nbtw 巴打係隻秋?  one man band 做哂 game/art/level/story/network design?</blockquote><br />\n我冇咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係做programming,level design同埋network <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上其他野都係PM佢地傾完再同我講番<br />\n<br />\n至於中學個個唔講住先,因為未confirm既,就以我之前幫另一間中學做既vr app黎講,隻app主要係播一段英文或者係播片然後尋物,有限時有計分(當然係vr視點)<br />\n<br />\n實收都有五位數既,做就大約2個禮拜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己就興趣所致, 私底下寫過兩隻 2D game, 當然係無乜graphic, 淨係 dem到gameplay mechanism 個款, 自己玩下無搞咁多<br />\n<br />\n做VR/AR 難度會唔會高好多?"},{"pid":"ca3333eaab35bb6edf0de4a45d82a376406c1005","tid":235512,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T05:53:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bb6fb372d70e12aa0fb2fd42dd96d110de940e2","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:01:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打黎緊接個隻中學3D game 收佢幾錢<br />\n<br />\n想大約知下咩市價<br />\n<br />\nbtw 巴打係隻秋?  one man band 做哂 game/art/level/story/network design?</blockquote><br />\n我冇咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係做programming,level design同埋network <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上其他野都係PM佢地傾完再同我講番<br />\n<br />\n至於中學個個唔講住先,因為未confirm既,就以我之前幫另一間中學做既vr app黎講,隻app主要係播一段英文或者係播片然後尋物,有限時有計分(當然係vr視點)<br />\n<br />\n實收都有五位數既,做就大約2個禮拜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己就興趣所致, 私底下寫過兩隻 2D game, 當然係無乜graphic, 淨係 dem到gameplay mechanism 個款, 自己玩下無搞咁多<br />\n<br />\n做VR/AR 難度會唔會高好多?</blockquote><br />\n唔知上面位巴打介唔介意我講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面位巴打依加都問緊我關於2D character control,其實2D game複雜程度不下於3D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都係興趣係寫Program所以先做呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ngraphic就無咩所謂既,反正唔係我地要處理<br />\n<br />\n而VR同AR兩款我認為AR難度在於處理Scan呢一部份,其他都只係同做普通3D Game一樣<br />\n<br />\n而普通VR亦都唔係好難,最難係做user friendly呢部份,因為VR係使用方面有好大限制<br />\n但係你話Gear或者VIVE呢類型既VR既話就緊係站於難度既頂端啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe6b00237656c385c14246742d57494e1f4742b","tid":235512,"uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打黎緊接個隻中學3D game 收佢幾錢<br />\n<br />\n想大約知下咩市價<br />\n<br />\nbtw 巴打係隻秋?  one man band 做哂 game/art/level/story/network design?</blockquote><br />\n我冇咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係做programming,level design同埋network <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上其他野都係PM佢地傾完再同我講番<br />\n<br />\n至於中學個個唔講住先,因為未confirm既,就以我之前幫另一間中學做既vr app黎講,隻app主要係播一段英文或者係播片然後尋物,有限時有計分(當然係vr視點)<br />\n<br />\n實收都有五位數既,做就大約2個禮拜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己就興趣所致, 私底下寫過兩隻 2D game, 當然係無乜graphic, 淨係 dem到gameplay mechanism 個款, 自己玩下無搞咁多<br />\n<br />\n做VR/AR 難度會唔會高好多?</blockquote><br />\n唔知上面位巴打介唔介意我講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面位巴打依加都問緊我關於2D character control,其實2D game複雜程度不下於3D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都係興趣係寫Program所以先做呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ngraphic就無咩所謂既,反正唔係我地要處理<br />\n<br />\n而VR同AR兩款我認為AR難度在於處理Scan呢一部份,其他都只係同做普通3D Game一樣<br />\n<br />\n而普通VR亦都唔係好難,最難係做user friendly呢部份,因為VR係使用方面有好大限制<br />\n但係你話Gear或者VIVE呢類型既VR既話就緊係站於難度既頂端啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打好利害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我未同人夾過, 覺得要夾仲難過自己一腳踢, 自己一個諗D野點行個logic已經R爆頭 (當然係因為我廢)<br />\n<br />\n淨係3D model, 貼圖, gameplay, UI 呢D要夾好已經好難, 莫講話將兩個人寫既code 擺埋一齊行"},{"pid":"e640d2a73230f9d28058328f5c21db2542a08c8c","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打黎緊接個隻中學3D game 收佢幾錢<br />\n<br />\n想大約知下咩市價<br />\n<br />\nbtw 巴打係隻秋?  one man band 做哂 game/art/level/story/network design?</blockquote><br />\n我冇咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係做programming,level design同埋network <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上其他野都係PM佢地傾完再同我講番<br />\n<br />\n至於中學個個唔講住先,因為未confirm既,就以我之前幫另一間中學做既vr app黎講,隻app主要係播一段英文或者係播片然後尋物,有限時有計分(當然係vr視點)<br />\n<br />\n實收都有五位數既,做就大約2個禮拜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己就興趣所致, 私底下寫過兩隻 2D game, 當然係無乜graphic, 淨係 dem到gameplay mechanism 個款, 自己玩下無搞咁多<br />\n<br />\n做VR/AR 難度會唔會高好多?</blockquote><br />\n唔知上面位巴打介唔介意我講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面位巴打依加都問緊我關於2D character control,其實2D game複雜程度不下於3D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都係興趣係寫Program所以先做呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ngraphic就無咩所謂既,反正唔係我地要處理<br />\n<br />\n而VR同AR兩款我認為AR難度在於處理Scan呢一部份,其他都只係同做普通3D Game一樣<br />\n<br />\n而普通VR亦都唔係好難,最難係做user friendly呢部份,因為VR係使用方面有好大限制<br />\n但係你話Gear或者VIVE呢類型既VR既話就緊係站於難度既頂端啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打好利害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我未同人夾過, 覺得要夾仲難過自己一腳踢, 自己一個諗D野點行個logic已經R爆頭 (當然係因為我廢)<br />\n<br />\n淨係3D model, 貼圖, gameplay, UI 呢D要夾好已經好難, 莫講話將兩個人寫既code 擺埋一齊行</blockquote><br />\n同人夾基本上都要一段時間磨合既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇人係石頭爆出黎就識coding既,coding呢d慢慢黎就得架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相反design方面就比較睇個人既概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb2e0647ba0b20cd4e2dd8fd2d64de4d9522c0f","tid":235512,"uid":2107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:31:12.000Z","msg":"巴打會自己畫model 定用asset store 個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e4eadaa6e7cd5c6e5942cec106c7de27ddbe1e","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:41:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打會自己畫model 定用asset store 個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我頂多可以bulid下場,model就真係唔識所以都係asset store為主<br />\n<br />\n當然亦都有同其他人夾既model<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef776c9d00ccfc56c3cd194d1f12a2779b69803","tid":235512,"uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:44:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n其實我依加仲係學生黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上堂學就學左大約半年,我學第一個月既時侯覺得學得太慢,然後開始一有時間就睇下相關既片同埋自己寫下d program出黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後拎左d作品去見工又真係見得成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咩地方搵工見?<br />\n<br />\n香港無乜gaming studio"},{"pid":"fca6533069b2a570bb991b4e1a65e71dbbca3824","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n其實我依加仲係學生黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上堂學就學左大約半年,我學第一個月既時侯覺得學得太慢,然後開始一有時間就睇下相關既片同埋自己寫下d program出黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後拎左d作品去見工又真係見得成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咩地方搵工見?<br />\n<br />\n香港無乜gaming studio</blockquote><br />\n第一份job係學校推薦既,跟住之後個d有係學校介紹又有係之前公司介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基本上係香港比較少game方面既job可以做,大多數做都係小遊戲(roadshow)為主<br />\n所以gaming studio我都好少接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f5c2f6f6e1ff0499c12a817b6994ef67f558a2","tid":235512,"uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20