00Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n其實我依加仲係學生黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上堂學就學左大約半年,我學第一個月既時侯覺得學得太慢,然後開始一有時間就睇下相關既片同埋自己寫下d program出黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後拎左d作品去見工又真係見得成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咩地方搵工見?<br />\n<br />\n香港無乜gaming studio</blockquote><br />\n第一份job係學校推薦既,跟住之後個d有係學校介紹又有係之前公司介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基本上係香港比較少game方面既job可以做,大多數做都係小遊戲(roadshow)為主<br />\n所以gaming studio我都好少接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nVTC?</blockquote><br />\n係,不過都係個句,讀完十個有九個冇工開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港呢行實在太窄, 睇下人地外國 d studio 幾撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n初初都有諗住將興趣發展成事業, 因為一黎可以Home office, 二黎就算考慮移民唔住香港, 例如台灣, 都可以賺香港既錢係第二度洗, 襟洗好多<br />\n<br />\n但係計一計條數, 如果我將學寫game 既時間, 擺番係自己做開個行度, 效益應該大好多<br />\n<br />\n就咁放棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e40381b154de7d9627dc161d7bbfc5a1ef502c3","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T07:17:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n其實我依加仲係學生黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上堂學就學左大約半年,我學第一個月既時侯覺得學得太慢,然後開始一有時間就睇下相關既片同埋自己寫下d program出黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後拎左d作品去見工又真係見得成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咩地方搵工見?<br />\n<br />\n香港無乜gaming studio</blockquote><br />\n第一份job係學校推薦既,跟住之後個d有係學校介紹又有係之前公司介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基本上係香港比較少game方面既job可以做,大多數做都係小遊戲(roadshow)為主<br />\n所以gaming studio我都好少接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nVTC?</blockquote><br />\n係,不過都係個句,讀完十個有九個冇工開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港呢行實在太窄, 睇下人地外國 d studio 幾撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n初初都有諗住將興趣發展成事業, 因為一黎可以Home office, 二黎就算考慮移民唔住香港, 例如台灣, 都可以賺香港既錢係第二度洗, 襟洗好多<br />\n<br />\n但係計一計條數, 如果我將學寫game 既時間, 擺番係自己做開個行度, 效益應該大好多<br />\n<br />\n就咁放棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger,應該咁講,係亞洲地區真係做Game呢行都係乞食多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除非入到大公司或者你自己開studio但係你又做到成績出黎啦,不過1000個人入面有幾多個係真係做到就唔講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過真係睇自己興趣,我自己覺得我依加夠我洗而又做得幾開心,所以暫時都會繼續做落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於移民我都有諗過,不過至少係香港做多幾年,搵多d經驗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0191b2828524e8983810b6a5b3cf42928c767f31","tid":235512,"uid":8750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T07:57:41.000Z","msg":"搭單問樓主有冇web freelance介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ab3342fcde6ecee30966efb9c4ccc73e5fb9c2","tid":235512,"uid":115538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T08:14:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問樓主有冇web freelance介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣又真係冇,Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74202232ae3051c806c7fd27a4dab4670b40b34","tid":235512,"uid":102405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T10:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無咩 state machine library